text: Armonía "Nya" Quesada (13 April 1919 – 6 December 2013) was an Argentine actress. Her career lasted for almost fifty years. Quesada died on 6 December 2013 from natural causes, aged 94, in Buenos Aires.Murió la actriz Nya Quesada ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1919 births Category:2013 deaths Category:Argentine movie actors Category:Argentine television actors Category:Argentine stage actors Category:Actors from Buenos Aires Category:People from Bahía Blanca
